              "is_public": true,
              "text": "# Monitoring the State of the System\nWe'll introduce:\n1. [CloudFlare](https://www.cloudflare.com/) for improved DNS with monitoring and failover capabilities.\n2. [DataDog](https://www.datadoghq.com/product/) for stack performance and health status.\n\nAWS also has native tools to help monitor performance called [CloudWatch](https://aws.amazon.com/cloudwatch/).",
